==================================================
PERSONALIZATION ENGINE
==================================================

This is critical.

System must answer:

- what should the user do today?
- what is overdue?
- what is weakest pattern?
- is user improving vs past self?
- is solve time decreasing?
- is solution quality improving?

Implement:

UserTrainingProfile
- goals
- time per day
- difficulty mix
- weak patterns

TrainingContract
- daily requirements
- weekly targets
- focus time

DailyMission
- required tasks
- optional tasks
- review tasks

PerformanceSnapshot
- avg solve time
- attempts
- hint usage
- improvement trends

ProblemPerformance
- first solve time
- best solve time
- latest solve time
- attempts
- complexity (self-reported)
- confidence

MVP:
- complexity tracking is manual

==================================================
MVP FLOWS
==================================================

Flow 1: Neovim startup
- plugin calls local agent
- if not practiced → notify

Flow 2: Timer
- start timer from Neovim
- persist in local agent

Flow 3: Submit
- plugin → agent → server → worker → verdict

Flow 4: Daily mission
- system generates tasks
- agent exposes them
- plugin shows them

